name: Google Drive
SQL: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `googledrive` (`id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,`key` text,`userid` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,`status` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`), timestamp TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,UNIQUE KEY `userid` (`userid`)) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=13 ;
